{
  "title": "People Are Calling Out This Edited Picture Of Demi Lovato For Body-Shaming Her",
  "content": "<div><div><div class=\"js-subbuzz-wrapper\">\n                    <div>\n                      <div class=\"subbuzz subbuzz-instagram\n  \n  \n  \n  \n  \">\n\n                        <div id=\"9723372\" class=\"subbuzz-anchor\"></div>\n\n\n                        <b class=\"subbuzz__header\">\n\n\n\n                          <span class=\"js-subbuzz__title-text\">A few months ago, Vladimir Serbanescu, a 17-year-old\n                            artist from Romania, drew this image of Demi Lovato as a mermaid and shared it on\n                            Instagram.</span>\n\n                        </b>\n\n\n                        <figure>\n\n\n                          <div class=\"subbuzz__media-container\">\n                            <div class=\"cls-min-ratio\">\n                              <div>\n                                <blockquote class=\"js-instagram__container instagram__container\">\n\n\n\n                                  <a class=\"subbuzz-embed__placeholder subbuzz__media-link\" href=\"https://instagram.com/p/BIIivW-DEWO/\">\n                                    <img class=\"subbuzz__media-image\" src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAIBRAA7\" alt=\"Instagram\">\n\n                                    <div class=\"subbuzz__media-cta\">\n\n                                      View this photo on Instagram\n\n                                    </div>\n                                  </a>\n                                </blockquote>\n                              </div>\n                            </div>\n                            <div class=\"subbuzz__figure-footer\">\n\n\n\n                              <span class=\"subbuzz__attribution\n    subbuzz__attribution--component\n    js-subbuzz__attribution\n    \">\n                                <a href=\"https://instagram.com/p/BIIivW-DEWO/#author_vladyart\">Instagram: @vladyart</a>\n                              </span>\n\n\n\n                              \n\n\n\n                            </div>\n                          </div>\n                        </figure>\n                      </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <div></div>\n                  </div><div class=\"js-subbuzz-wrapper\">\n                    <div>\n\n\n                      <div class=\"subbuzz subbuzz-image\n  \n  \n  \n  \n  \">\n\n                        <div id=\"9723375\" class=\"subbuzz-anchor\"></div>\n\n\n\n                        <b class=\"subbuzz__header\">\n\n\n\n                          <span class=\"js-subbuzz__title-text\">The drawing recently resurfaced – and it\n                            didn't go down too well with the singer. Lovato commented on a repost of the photo\n                            saying that although the drawing was \"gorgeous\" it was not how her body\n                            looks.</span>\n\n                        </b>\n\n\n\n\n                        <figure class=\"subbuzz__media\">\n\n\n                          <div class=\" subbuzz__media--full-width-container\">\n\n                            <div class=\"subbuzz__media-container js-subbuzz__media-container\n          subbuzz__media-container--small-margin-bottom\n          \">\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n                              <picture>\n                                <source srcset=\"https://img.buzzfeed.com/buzzfeed-static/static/2016-10/3/6/asset/buzzfeed-prod-fastlane03/sub-buzz-13798-1475491187-7.png?downsize=700%3A%2A&amp;output-quality=auto&amp;output-format=auto 1600w\" width=\"625\" height=\"402\">\n\n                                <source srcset=\"https://img.buzzfeed.com/buzzfeed-static/static/2016-10/3/6/asset/buzzfeed-prod-fastlane03/sub-buzz-13798-1475491187-7.png?downsize=700%3A%2A&amp;output-quality=auto&amp;output-format=auto 800w\" width=\"933\" height=\"600\">\n\n\n                                <img src=\"https://img.buzzfeed.com/buzzfeed-static/static/2016-10/3/6/asset/buzzfeed-prod-fastlane03/sub-buzz-13798-1475491187-7.png?downsize=700%3A%2A&amp;output-quality=auto&amp;output-format=auto\" alt=\"\" class=\"subbuzz__media-image--static subbuzz-picture js-subbuzz__media js-pinnable\" width=\"625\" height=\"402\">\n                              </picture>\n\n                            </div>\n                          </div>\n                          <div class=\"subbuzz__figure-footer\">\n\n\n\n                            <span class=\"subbuzz__attribution\n    subbuzz__attribution--component\n    js-subbuzz__attribution\n    \">\n                              sexlikelovato_ / Instagram\n                            </span>\n\n\n\n                            \n\n\n\n                          </div>\n\n\n                        </figure>\n\n                      </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <div></div>\n                  </div><div class=\"js-subbuzz-wrapper\">\n                    <div>\n\n                      <div class=\"subbuzz subbuzz-text\n  \n  \n  \n  \n  \">\n\n                        <div id=\"9725421\" class=\"subbuzz-anchor\"></div>\n\n\n\n                        <b class=\"subbuzz__header\">\n\n\n\n                          <span class=\"js-subbuzz__title-text\">She wrote: \"Is that how my boobs should look?\n                            It's gorgeous but that's not my body 😕\"</span>\n\n                        </b>\n\n\n\n                        <p>Lovato has <a href=\"https://www.buzzfeed.com/kelleydunlap/how-demi-lovato-learned-to-love-her-body?utm_term=.ve1eXp066a#.bf4PQkDBBz\">previously</a>\n                          spoken out about her body image, as well as her eating disorder.</p>\n                        <p>\"I’ve been open about my struggles because part of my recovery includes being\n                          honest with myself and others, and I’m inspired to use my success as a platform to help\n                          others suffering,\" she <a href=\"https://www.buzzfeed.com/kelleydunlap/how-demi-lovato-learned-to-love-her-body?utm_term=.dfl8pMK1Vp#.pjPOd7qx1d\">told\n                            BuzzFeed</a> last year.</p>\n\n                      </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <div></div>\n                  </div><div class=\"js-subbuzz-wrapper\">\n                    <div>\n                      <div class=\"subbuzz subbuzz-instagram\n  \n  \n  \n  \n  \">\n\n                        <div id=\"9724118\" class=\"subbuzz-anchor\"></div>\n\n\n                        <b class=\"subbuzz__header\">\n\n\n\n                          <span class=\"js-subbuzz__title-text\">Lovato's comment upset Serbanescu, and he\n                            re-uploaded the drawing with a caption that said it wasn't intended to be a realistic\n                            image, and that he was no longer proud of his work.</span>\n\n                        </b>\n\n\n                        <figure>\n\n\n                          <div class=\"subbuzz__media-container\">\n                            <div class=\"cls-min-ratio\">\n                              <div>\n                                <blockquote class=\"js-instagram__container instagram__container\">\n\n\n\n                                  <a class=\"subbuzz-embed__placeholder subbuzz__media-link\" href=\"https://instagram.com/p/BK93syzB8rx/\">\n                                    <img class=\"subbuzz__media-image\" src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAIBRAA7\" alt=\"Instagram\">\n\n                                    <div class=\"subbuzz__media-cta\">\n\n                                      View this photo on Instagram\n\n                                    </div>\n                                  </a>\n                                </blockquote>\n                              </div>\n                            </div>\n                            <div class=\"subbuzz__figure-footer\">\n\n\n\n                              <span class=\"subbuzz__attribution\n    subbuzz__attribution--component\n    js-subbuzz__attribution\n    \">\n                                <a href=\"https://instagram.com/p/BK93syzB8rx/\">instagram.com</a>\n                              </span>\n\n\n\n                              \n\n\n\n\n\n                              <div class=\"subbuzz__description\n  \">\n                                <p>The caption read: </p>\n                                <p>\"If I make your waist slimmer and your boobs bigger to accentuate the fact that\n                                  I drew you as a mermaid, a mythological creature, doesn't mean I say that you\n                                  should look like that or all girls should look like that. That's how I imagine\n                                  mermaids. I worked a lot on that drawing and i was proud of it, but not anymore.\"\n                                </p>\n                              </div>\n\n                            </div>\n                          </div>\n                        </figure>\n                      </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <div></div>\n                  </div><div class=\"js-subbuzz-wrapper\">\n                    <div>\n\n\n                      <div class=\"subbuzz subbuzz-tweet xs-mb4\">\n                        <div id=\"9724823\" class=\"subbuzz-anchor\"></div>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n                        <b class=\"subbuzz__header\">\n\n\n\n                          <span class=\"js-subbuzz__title-text\">This led to another Twitter user editing the drawing to\n                            make Lovato's body appear larger. The image took off and went viral – one tweet\n                            of the same drawing shared by <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hisillusion/status/781883829942382592?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">@hisillusion</a> got over 40,000 retweets.</span>\n\n                        </b>\n\n                        <figure>\n                          <div class=\"cls-min-size\">\n                            <div class=\"js-tweet__container tweet__container\">\n                              <blockquote class=\"subbuzz-tweet__container js-tweet__placeholder\">\n\n                                <div class=\"subbuzz-tweet__tweet\">\n                                  <div class=\"subbuzz-tweet__byline\">\n                                    <img class=\"subbuzz-tweet__avatar\" src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/profile_images/762405851428753409/pst8Hjp2_normal.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"46\" height=\"46\">\n                                    <div class=\"subbuzz-tweet__author\">\n                                      <a class=\"subbuzz-tweet__display-name\" href=\"https://twitter.com/liquoronurlips\">J. Trump 👼🏻</a>\n                                      <a class=\"subbuzz-tweet__username\" href=\"https://twitter.com/liquoronurlips\">@liquoronurlips</a>\n                                    </div>\n                                  </div>\n\n                                  <p class=\"subbuzz-tweet__text\">Here bitch @ddlovato</p>\n\n                                  <time class=\"subbuzz-tweet__timestamp\">\n                                    <a class=\"subbuzz-tweet__created-at\" href=\"https://twitter.com/liquoronurlips/status/781874683289411588\">Fri Sep 30\n                                      15:13:45 UTC+0000 2016</a>\n                                  </time>\n\n                                  <div class=\"subbuzz-tweet__meta\">\n                                    <a class=\"subbuzz-tweet__meta-item subbuzz-tweet__reply\" href=\"https://twitter.com/intent/tweet?in_reply_to=781874683289411588\">Reply</a>\n                                    <a class=\"subbuzz-tweet__meta-item subbuzz-tweet__retweet\" href=\"https://twitter.com/intent/retweet?tweet_id=781874683289411588\">Retweet</a>\n                                    <a class=\"subbuzz-tweet__meta-item subbuzz-tweet__favorite\" href=\"https://twitter.com/intent/favorite?tweet_id=781874683289411588\">Favorite</a>\n                                  </div>\n                                </div>\n                              </blockquote>\n                            </div>\n                          </div>\n\n\n\n                          <figcaption class=\"subbuzz__caption\">\n\n\n\n                          </figcaption>\n                        </figure>\n                      </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <div></div>\n                  </div><div class=\"js-subbuzz-wrapper\">\n                    <div>\n\n\n                      <div class=\"subbuzz subbuzz-image\n  \n  \n  \n  \n  \">\n\n                        <div id=\"9724233\" class=\"subbuzz-anchor\"></div>\n\n\n\n                        <b class=\"subbuzz__header\">\n\n\n\n                          <span class=\"js-subbuzz__title-text\">The picture prompted a backlash, with many people quickly\n                            coming to Lovato's defence and saying she has consistently spoken about body\n                            positivity.</span>\n\n                        </b>\n\n\n\n\n                        <figure class=\"subbuzz__media\">\n\n\n                          <div class=\" js-full-size-image subbuzz__media--full-width-container\">\n\n                            \n\n                            <div class=\"subbuzz__media-container js-subbuzz__media-container\n          subbuzz__media-container--small-margin-bottom\n           js-progressive-image-container\">\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n                              <img class=\"subbuzz__media-image subbuzz__media-image--deferred\n  js-subbuzz__media js-progressive-image js-pinnable\" src=\"https://img.buzzfeed.com/buzzfeed-static/static/2016-10/3/9/asset/buzzfeed-prod-fastlane01/sub-buzz-22419-1475503150-1.png\" alt=\"\">\n\n                            </div>\n                          </div>\n                          <div class=\"subbuzz__figure-footer\">\n\n\n\n                            <span class=\"subbuzz__attribution\n    subbuzz__attribution--component\n    js-subbuzz__attribution\n    \">\n                              @delafro_ / Twitter / Via <a href=\"https://twitter.com/delafro_/status/782316864974323712\">Twitter: @delafro_</a>\n                            </span>\n\n\n\n                            \n\n\n\n                          </div>\n\n\n                        </figure>\n\n                      </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <div></div>\n                  </div><div class=\"js-subbuzz-wrapper\">\n                    <div>\n\n\n                      <div class=\"subbuzz subbuzz-image\n  \n  \n  \n  \n  \">\n\n                        <div id=\"9724247\" class=\"subbuzz-anchor\"></div>\n\n\n\n                        <b class=\"subbuzz__header\">\n\n\n\n                          <span class=\"js-subbuzz__title-text\">People said the edited drawing body-shamed Lovato, and\n                            that it was uncalled for as she had \"politely\" asked for the original drawing to\n                            reflect her real shape and size.</span>\n\n                        </b>\n\n\n\n\n                        <figure class=\"subbuzz__media\">\n\n\n                          <div class=\" js-full-size-image subbuzz__media--full-width-container\">\n\n                            \n\n                            <div class=\"subbuzz__media-container js-subbuzz__media-container\n          subbuzz__media-container--small-margin-bottom\n           js-progressive-image-container\">\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n                              <img class=\"subbuzz__media-image subbuzz__media-image--deferred\n  js-subbuzz__media js-progressive-image js-pinnable\" src=\"https://img.buzzfeed.com/buzzfeed-static/static/2016-10/3/10/asset/buzzfeed-prod-fastlane01/sub-buzz-22404-1475503340-12.png\" alt=\"\">\n\n                            </div>\n                          </div>\n                          <div class=\"subbuzz__figure-footer\">\n\n\n\n                            <span class=\"subbuzz__attribution\n    subbuzz__attribution--component\n    js-subbuzz__attribution\n    \">\n                              @intoalec / Twitter / Via <a href=\"https://twitter.com/intoalec/status/781922175011913728\">Twitter: @intoalec</a>\n                            </span>\n\n\n\n                            \n\n\n\n                          </div>\n\n\n                        </figure>\n\n                      </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <div></div>\n                  </div><div class=\"js-subbuzz-wrapper\">\n                    <div>\n\n\n                      <div class=\"subbuzz subbuzz-image\n  \n  \n  \n  \n  \">\n\n                        <div id=\"9724802\" class=\"subbuzz-anchor\"></div>\n\n\n\n                        <b class=\"subbuzz__header\">\n\n\n\n                          <span class=\"js-subbuzz__title-text\">Others tweeted that the edited drawing was harmful, and\n                            that Lovato was being unfairly targeted.</span>\n\n                        </b>\n\n\n\n\n                        <figure class=\"subbuzz__media\">\n\n\n                          <div class=\" js-full-size-image subbuzz__media--full-width-container\">\n\n                            \n\n                            <div class=\"subbuzz__media-container js-subbuzz__media-container\n          subbuzz__media-container--small-margin-bottom\n           js-progressive-image-container\">\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n                              <img class=\"subbuzz__media-image subbuzz__media-image--deferred\n  js-subbuzz__media js-progressive-image js-pinnable\" src=\"https://img.buzzfeed.com/buzzfeed-static/static/2016-10/3/10/asset/buzzfeed-prod-fastlane02/sub-buzz-31362-1475505903-1.png\" alt=\"\">\n\n                            </div>\n                          </div>\n                          <div class=\"subbuzz__figure-footer\">\n\n\n\n                            <span class=\"subbuzz__attribution\n    subbuzz__attribution--component\n    js-subbuzz__attribution\n    \">\n                              @TRAINWRECKSTAN / Twitter / Via <a href=\"https://twitter.com/TRAlNWRECKSTAN/status/781894722650533888\">Twitter: @TRAlNWRECKSTAN</a>\n                            </span>\n\n\n\n                            \n\n\n\n                          </div>\n\n\n                        </figure>\n\n                      </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <div></div>\n                  </div><div class=\"js-subbuzz-wrapper\">\n                    <div>\n\n                      <div class=\"subbuzz subbuzz-text\n  \n  \n  \n  \n  \">\n\n                        <div id=\"9725562\" class=\"subbuzz-anchor\"></div>\n\n\n\n                        <b class=\"subbuzz__header\">\n\n\n\n                          <span class=\"js-subbuzz__title-text\">Still, Lovato will continue to slay, either as a human or\n                            mermaid.</span>\n\n                        </b>\n\n\n\n\n\n                      </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <div></div>\n                  </div></div></div>",
